tid":1103353,"uid":33874,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T15:57:45.000Z","msg":"係人睇到個真正漏洞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢報上去90，實偷唔知，但我係佢就實報細數<br />\n公司check完都係無咗80，即係有10其實佢係唔洗報，換返做錢就十幾萬<br />\n佢話前後加埋偷咗4個月，即係平均一個月其實可以拎走兩三萬而無人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢做26年，有乜位偷到雞肯定知<br />\n<br />\n周生生又係嘅，俾得15k人，俾我都偷你啦"},{"pid":"2335ecb9f3a8540b4cfeed7b9b35795c87e70b97","tid":1103353,"uid":22913,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T15:58:15.000Z","msg":"年年賺幾億 技工26年經驗萬五人工<br />\n真係抵個老細會發達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"479c5c33e42eb7ccfca2ec3200124141b9285319","tid":1103353,"uid":42246,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"075ca36cb8c1eae9edb448209a925950ce97e83f","tid":1103353,"uid":10757,"like":89,"dislike":4,"score":85,"quote":{"pid":"1b066981a900bcf0b164985d1033a124778fc9f7","tid":1103353,"uid":78304,"like":146,"dislike":1,"score":145,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T10:57:35.000Z","msg":"做成26年先得咁低人工，唔怪得佢咁早。不過佢醒既用呢個方法買3號仔，領展應該幾和味"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:01:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T16:13:42.000Z","msg":"但100萬 話多又唔係好多<br />\n搞到又有案底 又冇左份工 又坐22個月<br />\n<br />\n我係佢一定繼續偷落去 再拎去賭<br />\n一係我發達（再偷偷地填返數）<br />\n 一係我比人捉（下半世食皇家飯）<br />\n<br />\n依家唔上唔落唔知做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d7fc5290ec532fc9cd35a098d99d84cea436e19","tid":1103353,"uid":82816,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T16:31:37.000Z","msg":"坐完成行都無人請架啦<br />\n為左100萬 成26年經驗白廢 點解咁多人話值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"013e0e15aeeac937b7ce44bf1111648472217685","tid":1103353,"uid":78304,